Overview

Cisco Catalyst C9200L-48T-4G-A is a next-generation stackable switch. It has 48  Ethernet 10/100/1000 ports and 2x 10G SFP+ uplink interfaces. It is designed to provide the highest-density stacking bandwidth approach in the market, as well as the most adaptable uplink architecture. Cisco C9200L-48T-4G-A  Switch comes with 20G stack bandwidth, 95.2 Mpps forwarding performance, 216 Gbps stacking bandwidth along with 512 MB RAM and 128 MB flash memory.
